    n\u0103ng (moves)</color=red> c\u1EE7a pokemon:\n  + K\u1EF9 n\u0103ng c\xF3
    <color=red>h\u1EC7, power, pp(s\u1ED1 l\u1EA7n s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng)</color=red>\n 
